headline: Amazon, Alphabet, and Super Micro Shares Are Falling, What You Need To Know
summary: A number of stocks fell in the morning session after President Trump criticized the Federal Reserve's approach to interest rate cuts, warning that the pace was slow and could hinder economic growth. Trump's comments added pressure to an already sensitive market, raising concerns about political interference in monetary policy.

headline: Prediction: Super Micro Computer Could Surge by 150% in the Next Year
summary: Most investors came to know Super Micro as one of the biggest artificial intelligence winners, at least through the first half of last year.  Despite all of this, Super Micro has actually refuted a lot of the allegations against it, and it's also very well positioned to capture the next wave of AI investment.  First, the best news for Super Micro is that its new auditor appears to have cleared its books as accurate, despite the resignation of former auditor Ernst & Young last October.
